00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:03,359
With neither driver having
raced on a tarmac circuit before,

277
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,559
it's a solid debut.

278
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:07,839
Ollie crossing the line
sixth in class...

279
00:17:07,840 --> 00:17:09,559
Go on, Louis!

