00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:39,399
You can come in and win the race and
you'll be wanting more. Yeah.

291
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,759
So tomorrow, we go again.

292
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:44,960
Well done, boys.
Well done, well done, well done.

293
00:17:48,320 --> 00:17:51,399
Literally, I just want to
go out right now and just race,

294
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,199
to get all my frustration out.

295
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:56,119
There's no time
to dwell on mistakes,

296
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:58,960
training for the drivers
is constant.

297
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:04,319
Every time they get
behind the wheel, it's followed up

