00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:33,159
Hide it in there,
no-one'll know. Yeah.

378
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:35,679
Your first F1 race, what
was going through your mind?

379
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,839
Oh, so much.

380
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,719
I was so nervous back then. Yeah.

381
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:41,999
Bit of a twitchy bum?
Oh, definitely, definitely!

382
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:44,559
A lot of it is just pressure
you put on yourself.

383
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:47,119
You know you'll be able to do well
if you just go out there

