00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:39,439
Growing up, I spent a lot of
time on simulators.

403
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,959
Oh, look at this, lads.

404
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:45,239
Especially starting off, when you're
new into the world of racing

