00:24:21,040 --> 00:24:23,160
Makes it look easy, don't he?
I know, yeah.

414
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:28,639
So, that was my lap.

415
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:30,239
My one lap.

416
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:33,719
A 1:38.520.

417
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:37,359
Not my best lap I've ever done
but it was pretty good.

