00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:53,479
How much seat time on a sim
do you do a week?

438
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:56,160
A day at least on the simulator,
preparing for every weekend.

439
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:03,679
So, when you're stepping in,
instead of leaving this leg

