00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:14,079
Nice work.

442
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:15,799
Nice work, guys.

443
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:16,920
Great job.

444
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:20,399
But their car control's good.

445
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:22,119
What do we have at the moment?

