Adapting to a new car,

449
00:26:27,600 --> 00:26:29,959
a quicker car than what they're
used to driving.

450
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,760
Good work, lads, good work.

451
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:37,719
The team's been given
a taste of the big leagues,

452
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:40,000
and have shown real spirit doing it.

453
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:45,040
It's the spirit they'll need
for this experiment's final test.

