00:27:00,720 --> 00:27:03,400
Lando, if you'll do the
honours on that corner, pal.

459
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:10,840
570S GT4.

460
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:15,999
450hp, 3.8l,

461
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:20,199
north of 180mph.

462
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:21,719
I'm lost for words.

463
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,039
The MX-5s were brilliant,

