00:27:23,040 --> 00:27:25,200
and now we've gone the complete
opposite end.

465
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:30,039
Excitement, nerves,
the opportunity's amazing.

466
00:27:30,040 --> 00:27:32,359
I can't believe I'm actually
going to drive it.

467
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:34,519
Just want to get out there,
do my best.

468
00:27:34,520 --> 00:27:36,399
Yeah, I've got a new challenge.

469
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:39,119
They're a bit crazy for trusting
Ollie and Louis with it.

