602
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:55,399
Already it feels just right.

603
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,520
What a thing!

604
00:35:58,440 --> 00:35:59,879
It's so impressive.

605
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:02,360
You'd swear it was four-wheel drive.

