609
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:20,759
The front of the car is just superb.

610
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:24,999
It's so obedient.
You just turn, it goes.

611
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:28,719
And best of all, I don't feel
totally ashamed driving it

612
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:33,759
because it wasn't styled
by a seven-year-old.

613
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:35,959
Honda has nailed it with this thing.

614
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:38,960
It's a proper hot hatch.

615
00:36:40,480 --> 00:36:42,399
Hello-hello?

616
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,920
Look at this lot.

617
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:52,039
Hello. Andrew. To what do I owe this
