similar price to Chris' Civic.

659
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:21,440
And I've got to say,
this is a lot more special.

660
00:39:27,040 --> 00:39:31,199
Tolman's gone to town
on every inch of this Peugeot.

661
00:39:31,200 --> 00:39:34,759
The engine's
been totally overhauled.

662
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:37,279
There's stronger brakes,
new suspension.

663
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:40,600
They've even updated
the old interior.

664
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:47,159
