out in our favour.

872
00:53:30,160 --> 00:53:31,879
How was it? It was fun.

873
00:53:31,880 --> 00:53:34,399
So much fun, yeah.
You looked great out there.

874
00:53:34,400 --> 00:53:36,799
I could hear you saying the guy
in front of you was slower.

