00:54:17,200 --> 00:54:18,480
Go on, Ol, push!

883
00:54:22,200 --> 00:54:25,680
Come on, Ollie, bring it home, son.
Bring it home.

884
00:54:31,520 --> 00:54:34,360
Yes! Yeah, boy.

885
00:54:35,960 --> 00:54:38,159
Good lad.

886
00:54:38,160 --> 00:54:41,679
Well done, lad.
P7. Well done, mate.

887
00:54:41,680 --> 00:54:45,959
Good job. Thank you.
Fantastic. Fantastic.

