00:55:12,280 --> 00:55:15,959
I'm just so happy that we got
a good result for the team.

895
00:55:15,960 --> 00:55:18,199
Yeah, I'm just amazed.

896
00:55:18,200 --> 00:55:22,679
Wow, it's been incredible. We didn't
start out as racing drivers,

897
00:55:22,680 --> 00:55:25,679
but we've definitely finished
as one.

898
00:55:25,680 --> 00:55:27,679
It's been so incredible.

899
00:55:27,680 --> 00:55:30,199
It's like something
you're never going to forget,

900
00:55:30,200 --> 00:55:32,199
being here, doing all of this.

901
00:55:32,200 --> 00:55:35,199
The paddock team
has just been amazing.

902
00:55:35,200 --> 00:55:38,039
I just want to thank them
so much for looking after me.

903
00:55:38,040 --> 00:55:41,719
The mechanics, especially,
for getting the car set up for me.

904
00:55:41,720 --> 00:55:45,679
Callum and Lillie, me two mechanics,
we have been on a journey.

905
00:55:45,680 --> 00:55:47,879
We've got some amazing memories
together

906
00:55:47,880 --> 00:55:50,560
and memories
that we'll cherish forever.

907
00:55:52,320 --> 00:55:54,959
It's just been amazing
from start to finish.

