00:55:54,960 --> 00:55:57,599
The dream for me is basically to do
what I've done the last couple

909
00:55:57,600 --> 00:55:59,439
of months, just as a living.

910
00:55:59,440 --> 00:56:03,440
The dream for the future will be to
continue in any form of motorsport.

911
00:56:23,440 --> 00:56:25,519
There we go.

912
00:56:25,520 --> 00:56:29,239
A couple of months ago,
we had an idea.

913
00:56:29,240 --> 00:56:34,119
Could we get four young people
together and get into racing,

914
00:56:34,120 --> 00:56:36,999
people who would never get a shot?

915
00:56:37,000 --> 00:56:39,520
And if we could, what would happen?

916
00:56:41,440 --> 00:56:43,079
There's your answer.

917
00:56:43,080 --> 00:56:46,239
And it just goes to show
the talent's out there.

918
00:56:46,240 --> 00:56:49,840
All they need is a chance.

919
00:56:57,320 --> 00:57:00,640
CHEERING AND APPLAUSE

