00:57:03,200 --> 00:57:08,680
Give it up for Lillie,
Callum, Ollie and Louis!

921
00:57:14,160 --> 00:57:17,199
Amazing. Respect to all of you.

922
00:57:17,200 --> 00:57:20,319
Eight weeks from a standing start
to racing in GT Cup,

923
00:57:20,320 --> 00:57:22,039
that is a hell of an effort.
Fantastic.

924
00:57:22,040 --> 00:57:24,599
I tell you what, when that flag
dropped at Donington,

925
00:57:24,600 --> 00:57:26,359
all the nerves kicked in.

926
00:57:26,360 --> 00:57:29,119
For me, it was like sending
your kids off to school

927
00:57:29,120 --> 00:57:31,599
for the first time,
but this time the kids are driving

928
00:57:31,600 --> 00:57:34,279
220-grand McLarens!
