Well done. Amazing.

932
00:57:44,880 --> 00:57:46,839
CHEERING AND APPLAUSE

933
00:57:46,840 --> 00:57:50,119
And it goes to prove that there's
real talent out there

934
00:57:50,120 --> 00:57:52,079
and I'm very proud
of that young team.

